1n-X%C3%ADch-B%C3%ADch-ph%C3%BA/poem-me7U_8vSr2qqarH3OBVAMw">Tiền Xích Bích phú - 前赤壁賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Th%E1%BB%A9c/author-ZsPeAEZWTH-jxxg2cYfLgg">Tô Thức</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADn-h%C3%A0nh-vi%E1%BB%85n-tu-thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng/poem-GtdmSoi6EuIHKcwHFkRN8g">Tín hành viễn tu thuỷ đồng - 信行遠修水筒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%A9-t%E1%BB%AD-Hoan-h%E1%BB%99i-th%C3%AD-tr%C3%BAng-ph%C3%B3-b%E1%BA%A3ng/poem-xRbuuoTSWkEL4ivSEJfXSQ">Tứ tử Hoan hội thí trúng phó bảng - 賜子懽會試中副榜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Xu%E1%BA%A5t-xa-2/poem-yR76ZzKHVjBQGZhKRrsNMA">Xuất xa 2 - 出車 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br></div>	</div>
